1.0.name: wordpress/trafficspaces-plugin
1.0.description:
The Trafficspaces Wordpress plugin helps you integrate ads easily into your Wordpress site. It allows you to setup the layout of your ad zones in the sidebar without needing to edit any code. Once it is setup, your ads will start to display automatically.

For comments, questions and support use this email technical@trafficspaces.com
